title: Lid to a jar

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a lid to a jar, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an upper perspective view of a lid to a jar showing the new design;
FIG. 2 is a top elevation view thereof, the bottom elevation being identical; and,
FIG. 3 is a side elevation view thereof, all side views of the lid being identical.
The broken lines in FIG. 1 showing a jar depict environmental subject matter only and form no part of the claimed design.
